title: Episode #48 - BIRTHDAY SPECIAL PODCAST
description: For my 41st B-Day, I sit down in the MANCAVE, after dinner at Benihanas, w/ My two sisters Annie & Kottie, Kotties Fiancce Mike, & my wife and talk about the time Kottie thought I peed on her, my goals, & Annie being single.
